OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FAn NHS trust failed to provide "safe
OL,8,Fcare and treatment" for a teenage girl
OL,9,Fwho died on hospital grounds after
OL,10,Frunning from her ward, a court heard.
OL,12,FEllame Ford-Dunn, 16, died after
OL,13,Fabsconding from Worthing Hospital
OL,14,Fwhilst she was a mental health
OL,15,Finpatient on 20 March 2022.
OL,17,FShe ran from the hospital and was not
OL,18,Fimmediately followed by a nurse due to
OL,19,F"confusion" and a lack of appropriate
OL,20,Fprocedure in place.
