OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FOn Monday, University Hospitals Sussex
OL,8,FNHS Trust (UHST) pleaded guilty to
OL,9,Ffailing to provide safe care and
OL,10,Ftreatment to Ellame which exposed her
OL,11,Fto a significant risk of "avoidable
OL,12,Fharm" at Brighton Magistrates' Court.
OL,14,FProsecuting for the Care Quality
OL,15,FCommission (CQC), James Marsland said:
OL,16,F"The trust failed to provide safe care
OL,17,Fand treatment to Ellame by not doing
OL,18,Feverything that was reasonably
OL,19,Fpracticable...
