OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,F"The prosecution accepts that in that
OL,8,Fparticular regard the defendant trust
OL,9,Fwas in a difficult position; there was
OL,10,Fno immediately available alternative
OL,11,Fat the time of admitting Ellame to
OL,12,FBluefin Ward," said Mr Marsland.
OL,14,FHe added: "No tier four was readily
OL,15,Favailable and the high demand for such
OL,16,Fbeds is a national issue."
OL,18,FEllame had suffered with severe mental
OL,19,Fhealth difficulties for some time
OL,20,Fprior to her stay at Worthing
OL,21,FHospital, the court heard.
