OL,7,FThe charge arose from the lack of
OL,8,Fclarity in the UHST guidelines for
OL,9,Fstaff about vulnerable patients
OL,10,Fabsconding.
OL,12,FWhen Ellame ran, the nurse she was
OL,13,Fwith did not immediately follow her,
OL,14,Finstead alerting other staff because
OL,15,Fshe had been told on handover not to
OL,16,Ffollow.
