OL,7,FThe CQC said that their confusion was
OL,8,F"a symptom of the failure to have a
OL,9,Fpolicy directive that such vulnerable
OL,10,Fpatients ought to be followed
OL,11,Fimmediately", which has since been
OL,12,Famended.
OL,14,FEllame was found by police later that
OL,15,Fevening close to the edge of hospital
OL,16,Fgrounds, and died despite CPR at the
OL,17,Fscene.
