OL,11,F"Our family will never be whole again,
OL,12,Fwherever we go and wherever we go
OL,13,Fthere is an Ellame-shaped hole in the
OL,14,Fworld."
OL,16,FChief nurse at UHST, Maggie Davies
OL,17,Fsaid: "The loss of Ellame was a
