OL,7,F"Ever since Ellame's death we have
OL,8,Fagreed that our 'missing person'
OL,9,Fpolicy, and training around it, was
OL,10,Fnot clear enough.
OL,12,F"We highlighted that, made
OL,13,Fimprovements, and today we accepted
OL,14,Fthe single charge relating to that
OL,15,Fpolicy.
OL,17,F"We are committed to working with our
OL,18,Fpartners to ensure there are better
OL,19,Fways to care for people who are at a
OL,20,Fpoint of such vulnerability and
OL,21,Fdistress."
